# Tools — Local Notes

Environment-specific configuration that shouldn't be shared.

## What Goes Here

- SSH hosts and aliases
- API keys references (not the keys themselves!)
- Preferred TTS voices
- Device names
- Any setup-specific details

## Example

```
### TTS
- Voice: "Nova" (ElevenLabs)
- Command: sag -v "Nova" -o /tmp/reply.mp3 "text"

### SSH
- home-server → 192.168.1.100, user: admin
```

---

Copy this file to `TOOLS.md` and fill in your details.
